divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving back from Mcdonalds with my girlfriend on clove road in montague new jersey. It was a starless night. I saw a light comung over the next hill and it came on very fast and I remember seeing heads in the windows. I do not remember the rest of the night. The next morning i went to the store to get newsapers to find out about the airplane crash. There was none.
Summary: I thought it was an airplane that was going to crash way too low and slow.
